1) compile and install nginx with the nginx-rtmp module
2) cp the nginx.conf (/usr/local/nginx/conf/nginx.conf)
3) install OBS studio 
4) Open settings and browse to Stream and set the Stream type to "Custom Streaming Server"
5) Set stream URL to `rtmp://<hostname where nginx is installed>/show`
4) Set stream_key to `radio`
5) copy the html in `view.html` somewhere we want to show video